label: Card Creation Fee
description: Fee charged for creating the card.

label: Select Card Creation Fee
description: Fee charged for creating a card for an accountholder with an address other than the default supported countries.

label: Next Day Funding
description: Fee charged for funds that will be available after forty-eight hours.

label: Same Day Funding
description: Fee charged for funds that will be available in twenty-four hours.

label: Instant Funding
description: Fee charged for funds that will be available instantly.

label: Funding
description: Fee charged to fund the card.

label: ATM Withdrawal Fee
description: Fee charged for an ATM withdrawal.

label: Foreign Currency ATM Withdrawal Fee
description: Fee charged for withdrawing funds from an ATM in a currency other than that of the card.

label: ATM Decline
description: Fee charged for attempting to withdrawal funds from an ATM without sufficient funds.

label: ATM Balance Inquiry
description: Fee charged for requesting a balance at an ATM.
